Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:04.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
