Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:59.06,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ直ぐに歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:07.14,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用なこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:21.66,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偽りないその目に映る暖かい光りを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:26.71,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,溢れる希望の中で今僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:32.16,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どれだけの愛に出逢えるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:38.97,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ時を今生きている愛すると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:44.31,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,思う喜び に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:59.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直地一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:07.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我這顆笨拙的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:21.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,感受著你的真誠雙眼所發出的溫暖光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:26.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴在滿溢而出的希望中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:32.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們究竟能遇見多深沉的愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:38.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活在當下 愛在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:44.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此想來 不禁欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天到了 說到夏天就少不了暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上做廣播體操
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃冷麥麵 吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去泳池游泳 吃中華涼麵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃冰棒 夏天是我的最愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打住一下 我是剛田猛男 正在讀高一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害呢 某種意義上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們在討論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要和猛男同學的朋友一起去海邊玩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請砂川同學 砂川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？砂川同學也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.55,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)\fad(0,800)}{\c&HE8E8E8&}我的海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？和猛男的女友以及她朋友一起去海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去啊 要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海啊 大海很大很遼闊 是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川 你是強制參加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生的泳衣 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不准來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣是用來游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到海邊就少不了女生的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男你也很期待女朋友的泳衣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和穿泳衣不為別的 只是為了游泳而來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要用奇怪的眼光看待這樣的大和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不會成為那種男人中的雜碎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你穿什麼泳衣都和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選哪個好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕你胸部這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腳不也挺漂亮的嘛 身材不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿這個如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高叉泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個果然不適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為猛男同學他很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}說的也是呢 對凜子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而跟他想比 我卻是幼兒體形..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.88,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有像猛男同學那樣的好身材
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說帥..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定不是高1的身材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像奧運舉重選手一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是凜子男朋友的泳衣會是什麼樣的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是學校泳裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是比賽用的吧 超級小的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像很能游的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是猛男同學讓我心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我也想讓他看得怦然心動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}想好好加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會想要讓男朋友心動一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女為悅己者容嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家一起幫凜子選泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個絕對會被人亂掀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯 不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 我進來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已經進來了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？要離家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做明天的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不重復準備需要跟你確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人份的帳篷和飯盒由我來帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是去海水浴吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一遇險也是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂有備而無患嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大和打來的 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男同學 發佈颱風特報了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颱風？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是晴天漢子所以沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂說因為我是晴天漢子所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我正在阿砂家裡準備明天的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在也正在準備呢 明天好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜 用來玩砍西瓜遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..太多了吧？裡面裝了多少個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有泳圈之類等到了海邊再充氣就好了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很占空間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 你真的沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候看到夕陽沉入大海的景象讓我備受感動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和大和一起看那種夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 天氣很晴朗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們過得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐電車和公車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期末考得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛問這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？大和 很熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好近..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮陽傘放這可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再借一頂過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男好厲害 一口氣就吹起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換衣服去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝呀吼~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海可是游泳砍西瓜抓螃蟹的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了找到了 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 大家都太可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像大叔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男也換成泳裝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂大海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是抓螃蟹 撈蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍西瓜 游泳游到筋疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曬出奇怪形狀的曬痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像地圖一樣曬脫皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在暑假結束的曬痕大賽中取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的大海是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？海坊主？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 靠近不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子 猛男同學會不會游太遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那片海裡游得像鯨魚的傢夥就是猛男同學吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和太陽太相襯了 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是看呆的時候吧 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要讓他怦然心動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這風衣要披到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 轉十圈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不看大和就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 猛男 反了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪裡啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左 左
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再左一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左 左
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 就這樣筆直走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有4步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 猛男 STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊 太晃神了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一下 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 那是進入水中也沒問題的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服嗎..布料真少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是布料很少的 用來游泳的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說它是衣服 確實是衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用來游泳的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？冷靜下來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了啊 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海可是個好地方 一起好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家來打沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來 我來 1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
