Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 觀眾好多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼情況..結束不了
