Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 下一個丟我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去吧 再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和也要玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}舉棋不定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}呀~呀~呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 加油是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和猛男同學直接肌膚接觸的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？大和 要這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拉著你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好羨慕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別落下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在和我們家孩子們玩耍啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個人好精壯的身子呀 渾身肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 跟我家那位不能比呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個腹肌 像製冰盒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 製冰盒什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 果然很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:06.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 差不多該上岸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很受歡迎啊
