Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}咖喱飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子 牙齒裡黏著玉米哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她為什麼這麼手忙腳亂啊 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一下 凜子 喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想讓他心動..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可還沒成功自己先心動得一塌糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很喜歡你男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性一咬牙直接貼上去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子會先死掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 那個..那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起去石灘那邊走走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石灘 可以噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想抓小螃蟹是吧 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:35.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}不是螃蟹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 我抓螃蟹可是好手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要踩上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想著自己 真難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點去啦 接下來我幫你弄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:47.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？大和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學都有好好注意身邊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只是光顧著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,器量真小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有那麼偉大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以坐在你旁邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的夕陽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我正是想要和大和一起看這樣的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..好想成為心胸像大海般遼闊的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直待在猛男同學身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:40.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}凜子 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為夕陽的緣故嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這臉上的溫度..這胸中的熱度..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也最喜歡猛男同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}噗通 噗通 噗通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在這啊 你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩煙火了哦 煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來還是沒有成功讓他心動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很努力的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然還是很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後大家再一起出來看煙花吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用穿浴衣的樣子讓猛男同學心動呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}凜子真鍥而不捨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 今天我好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大和一起觀賞的夕陽真讓人感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去煙花大會吧？大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花啊 不錯 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定要讓猛男同學心跳到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大和一起看煙花啊..一定也會很感動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 你喜歡看煙花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這兩人是牛頭不對馬嘴啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在他們很幸福的份上..
